one_reviews_text: It took 20 minutes to download the game bu then it won't install it and says please contact Oculus support. How do I do that?? There is nowhere or how to contact.
review_feedback:
The game installs great, perhaps it was a temporary problem. It was the version that passed the Oculus review, so, it must be fine.
Please contact us at sumalab@sumalab.com and we will give to you a free key, so you can try again.
